			<p class="extra-space">A traditional cable company, DIRECTV asked us to design an innovative video player experience for their new online streaming service. They needed a solution that not only gave users access to their favorite content, but also helped them discover something new.</p>
			<p>I led the UX design and concept for the video player and worked with a visual designer, animator, and develper to prototype our final concept for DIRECTV. While I didn't create the final UI for the prototype, I helped define the interaction desing and overall user experience for the video player. </p>
