			<h1>Designing for continuous play</h1>	
			<p>An important business goal for the video player was to keep people watching. I explored several web video player experiences to see how other services allowed for continuous play that felt natural and useful for users. I found that allowing users to browse and watch was a very common pattern and expectation in the video streaming domain. Leveraging the new behavior, I created a framework for our player that allowed users to either binge episodic conent easily or browse and discovery content without ever having to change what they were currently viewing.</p>
