		<div class="section">
			<h2 class="extra-space">User Testing</h2>
			<p>We tested two major concepts for the core video player interaction: Immersive Video Player (the video player takes over the entire screen and the users can browse content through a contextual drawer) VS. In-Page Video Player (the video player is a part of a larger page of content--users must scroll down to explore more content). The Results showed a larger preference for the Immersive Video Player. We used the testing to validate our design choice and ultimately went with the immersive experience.</p>
			<p>I also wrote up a A/B test script for our research team to conduct with users. I included example questions, objectives, hypothesis, and success criteria we were looking for.</p>
